  Text: |
    Slide 4. Lens Studio 
    [Show Lens Studio Image / Spectacles Image]
    
    > Lens Studio was originally created to serve AR Creators first. 
    
    > Lens Studio focused on AR from day one. It’s very light, it takes less than 5 seconds to build an app.
    
    > It’s fast. Testing your updates is instantaneous, and there is no Play and Wait like you are used to in Unity. 
    
    > Can you imagine how different your workflow is going to be and how much more productive you can be in testing and building experiences back to back?

